Attachments: 2020.09.04_CiM_reply_in_support_of motion_to_stay_civil_case.pdf 
Attached is the reply letter Maxwell's counsel filed in further support of her motion to stay case. 
Alarmingly, they come out and say that they believe she is one of the victims named in the indictment, teetering 
dangerously close to a violation of the protective order in our case. 
My plan is still to file our letter in support of a stay as is this evening. Please let me know if anyone would like to discuss 
or revise our letter further before filing. 
Thanks, 
EFTA00023012
